description: Stanley’s Northeast Bar Room is taking to the streets with the addition of a food truck, Stanley’s on Wheels.  Stanley’s on Wheels will be serving-up Stanley’s well known smoked BBQ beef brisket sandwich along with several other favorites including; Reuben sandwich, BBQ beef brisket nachos, soft pretzel sticks with homemade cheese sauce and Oreo brownies for dessert. Stanley’s on Wheels will bring a little slice of Nordeast to downtown Minneapolis four days each week.  You will also find Stanley’s on Wheels at many local parks and festivals throughout the summer!
name: Stanley's On Wheels
